<package name="perl-Filesys-Notify-Simple" project="openSUSE:Factory">
  <title>Simple and dumb file system watcher</title>
  <description>Filesys::Notify::Simple is a simple but unified interface to get
notifications of changes to a given filesystem path. It utilizes inotify2
on Linux and fsevents on OS X if they're installed, with a fallback to the
full directory scan if they're not available.

</description>
